Intuitive and secure, groestlwallet gives you complete control over your Groestlcoin. Send and receive Groestlcoin payments instantly, with the safest mobile wallet available.

groestlwallet connects directly to the Groestlcoin network. This means that there are no servers to get hacked or go down - your funds are always safe. Even if your phone is lost, damaged or stolen, you can easily recover your funds using your personal recovery phrase.


Features:

* Send and receive Groestlcoin payments in seconds, online or in person
* One button payments to Groestlcoin-accepting merchants and websites
* Store your Groestlcoin safely and securely using built in hardware encryption
* Simple recovery phrase enables you to recover funds when your device is lost or broken
* Direct Groestlcoin network client - no servers to get hacked or go down

groestlwallet is open source and free. Send any amount of coins to anyone in the world instantly.

